name: Dissertations of China (Wanfang Data)
description: Dissertations of China (DOC) contains information on research activities by graduate students and their graduate supervisors in China. The database includes Masters, Doctoral, and Post-doctoral dissertations and theses from KEY Chinese research institutions from 1986 onward. ** Note that NYU subscribes to the following categories: Philosophy/Politics/Law, Social Sciences, Economics/Finance, Education/Literature/Art. **
